<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Sam Frost has been open about her struggles with depression and anxiety. </p>

<p>And during Sunday's episode of The All New Monty: Guys and Gals, the Home And Away star suffered a panic attack during rehearsals for the show. </p>

<p>'The word sexy has been used a lot and it makes me feel incredibly anxious,' Sam admitted before the dance practice started. </p>

<p>Stressed: Sam Frost (pictured) has been open about her struggles with depression and anxiety. And during Sunday's episode of The All New Monty: Guys and Gals, the Home And Away star suffered a panic attack during rehearsals for the show</p>

<p>'I panic and my chest gets heavy and I feel I need to leave the room or cry. It's incredibly challenging. I felt a little bit nervous'. </p>

<p>Afterwards, the former Bachelorette star felt that she was beginning to panic.  </p>

<p>'The fun thing about having anxiety is you never know when it's going to come on. I think performing in front of the group made me feel incredibly anxious. </p>

<p>Difficult: 'I feel a bit off. I feel a bit wonky at the moment,' Sam confessed, before she left the room to cry</p>

<p>She explained: 'I panic and my chest gets heavy and I feel I need to leave the room or cry. It's incredibly challenging. I felt a little bit nervous'</p>

<p>Tears: Breaking down and mopping away her tears, she was comforted by actress and fellow Monty performer Georgie Gardener</p>

<p>'I feel a bit off. I feel a bit wonky at the moment,' Sam confessed, before she left the room to cry. </p>

<p>Breaking down and mopping away her tears, she was comforted by actress and fellow Monty performer Georgie Gardener. </p>

<p>'It's a battle I am personally forever facing is feeling comfortable in my own skin its really tough,' Sam said when she'd calmed down.  </p>

<p>Body confidence: 'It's a battle I am personally forever facing is feeling comfortable in my own skin its really tough,' Sam said when she'd calmed down</p>

<p>'And I know this is for a greater cause so I have to put that aside, but it is very challenging,' she added. </p>

<p>Sam was very honest in admitting, 'I have always struggled with self confidence and my body'. </p>

<p>The actress previously told Nova's Fitzy and Wippa of her performance: 'I was absolutely terrified, I was shaking, I was very anxious.' </p>

